{"tid":1629933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴正警告左膠，咪再阻住手足召喚神獸","createTime":"2019-10-06T10:56:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T12:09:24.000Z","uid":30835,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"41fd51cb4dbdbbfd9a969fb87917e3da41e7e8a5","tid":1629933,"uid":30835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:56:43.000Z","msg":"我警告你地咪再阻住手足申張正義<br />\n依家警察根本冇用，根本幫唔到我地彰顯公義<br />\n幾個月黎手足被斬至重傷輕傷，甚至影響一生既傷害<br />\n但係施暴者呢？咁多個都只係頭破血流比盡都係輕傷<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">公平咩？</span></span><br />\n今日女手足好大機會斷腳or死，而個的士司機點？<br />\n都只係頭破血流，就係你班左膠仲阻住手足彰顯公義？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">夠喇</span></span><br />\n影人大頭，口角之爭你阻擋冇所謂<br />\n但係手足受傷既話我地要<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以牙還牙，以眼還眼</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以牙還牙，以眼還眼</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以牙還牙，以眼還眼</span></span>"},{"pid":"83930712ba3e8285d3e7a84bd370fef7987964be","tid":1629933,"uid":30835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:58:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以牙還牙，以眼還眼</span></span>"},{"pid":"5128bf7f4ec4defe398e9239a1cac9a3d9840bc1","tid":1629933,"uid":275238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:59:00.000Z","msg":"阻膠死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c5b1e117b8206daa67ea2180c5eacbee2a29c5","tid":1629933,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:59:36.000Z","msg":"「認真」各位手足 借東風啊！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629930</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7b95552a76aae34866b803d78d858a2cb59a49a5","tid":1629933,"uid":30835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:59:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以牙還牙，以眼還眼</span></span>"},{"pid":"7918ff7febfae33b9ddc7da93633770d59586b04","tid":1629933,"uid":49979,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:02:22.000Z","msg":"我只可以話 <br />\n<br />\n平民係好難接受依樣野<br />\n<br />\n所以唯有內傷為主 斷手腳都ok<br />\n<br />\n但血流滿面就冇咁好睇"},{"pid":"27b4c5c2f081f3793c6700c1800871d9b03b29c8","tid":1629933,"uid":30835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:02:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以牙還牙，以眼還眼</span></span>"},{"pid":"ce04ab5e1db8498c39ead66eefe124ba613867fe","tid":1629933,"uid":30835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:11:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以牙還牙，以眼還眼</span></span>"},{"pid":"f52b0f5ae7a1851cf49dc54e45cd58bed1f631f5","tid":1629933,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:11:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c90a21c1d2f626c60393761f6e61237e7df30dd5","tid":1629933,"uid":216888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:15:09.000Z","msg":"關節"},{"pid":"230f3c037e124d36cca41b7158bc05f17a57ccad","tid":1629933,"uid":30835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:15:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以牙還牙，以眼還眼</span></span>"},{"pid":"fe9189406acf98fdb4acd631051af9d12fda3fc6","tid":1629933,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:15:32.000Z","msg":"係咁易執吓就得<br />\n驗唔到傷先贏到外部勢力支持<br />\n裝修可以還原，神獸就好難<br />\n你知鬼佬架啦，好睇重人權"},{"pid":"96400cbb229c15041b3461aa1075951a3e998976","tid":1629933,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:18:16.000Z","msg":"好睇重人權呀"},{"pid":"9735f2f82798712787dbe9e20a1efe61a7e0a89d","tid":1629933,"uid":30835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"